tasks.task: Choosing and building a high tunnel or greenhouse structure
subtasks: Consider the plants to be grown
Choose materials for the structure (polyfilm, polycarbonate, glass)
Understand material lifespan (5-7 years for polyfilm and polycarbonate)
Plan for venting and cooling systems to manage indoor temperature

tasks.task: Venting and cooling systems in high tunnels
subtasks: Install doors or rolling sides for air escape
Install vents in the top of the structure for summer heat relief
